title: Watch Run The Jewels Talk Weed, Bernie Sanders, Meow The Jewels On The Daily Show
text: Killer Mike and El-P are, collectively, one hell of a great musical force. And they're also two of the great talkers working in music today. So it's cool to see the two of them show up on a late-night show and not perform. Last night, the two of them were on Trevor Noah's Daily Show, … More »
